NAME
	skilldata

DESCRIPTION

	Read /bin/daemons/skilld.c for more information.

	/basic/living/skills.c is also helpful.

	Guild object may define skill data, otherwise default values
	are used for training speed and forgetting.

	SKILL NAMES: They can be max 12 characters long for now.
	Skill names should have only lower case letters, NOT spaces
	nor numbers! Skill names MUST be registered!

EXAMPLE
	Check module   ~graah/g/skill_data.c

SEE ALSO
	/doc/man/man5/skill_names, skills
